dc_description_s: This line shapefile represents rivers in Honduras. The Global Map Honduras version 2 was developed based on Global Map Specifications version 2.2. The data source was a 1:1,000,000 map image made in 2007.Global Map data were developed under the cooperation of National Geospatial Information Authorities (NGIAs) of respective countries and regions.

Direccion General de Catastro y Geografia, General Direction for Cadastre and Geography
